*gentoolkit-0.1.17 (03 Sep 2002)

  09 Sep 2002; phoen][x <phoenix@gentoo.org> gentoolkit-0.1.17-r1.ebuild,
  files/scripts/emerge-webrsync :

  Bumped to new version in order to force portage to reinstall gentoolkit.
  emerge-webrsync was broken - it checked /etc/make.conf for GENTOO_MIRRORS
  but the new baselayout doesn't set GENTOO_MIRRORS in /etc/make.conf.
  Fixed that with some python-magic from scripts/bootstrap.sh.

