*gentoolkit-0.1.16 (28 Jul 2002)

  02 Sep 2002; Brandon Low <lostlogic@gentoo.org> files/scripts/qpkg:

  Parse off trailing slash in qpkg.

  06 Aug 2002; Karl Trygve Kalleberg <karltk@gentoo.org> gentoolkit-0.1.16.ebuild files/digest-gentoolkit-0.1.16:

  The utility useflag has been removed, as it is, in its current 
  implementation, very _DANGEROUS_ (in some common cases, it empties your 
  /etc/make.conf). If you still want to use it, don't 
  upgrade beyound 0.1.15-r2. See #5777 for details.

  Old version kept for backwards compatibility.

*gentoolkit-0.1.15-r2 (28 Jul 2002)

